name: Liga Privada Unico Serie UF-4
additionalNotes:
USA CT Stalk Cut & Cured Sun Grown Habano wrapper.  Brazilian Mata Fina binder. Undisclosed filler. Rolled 2 years ago. Actually the "JD4" blend, which Drew Estate had renamed "MF4" for 18 months or so, but changed the name again to the "UF4" for this exclusive 10/27/11 release of 40 bundles of 25 at Casa de Montecristo. Casa De Montecristo is allowing pre-orders of a limited amount of 5-packs.
